Package: rtyp
Title: An R Package For Generating Typst Markup
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Barbier", , "joseph.barbierdarnal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: rtyp offers R functions that are translated into valid Typst markup and provides a large number of built-in tools for working with Typst units, alignments, or colors.
